00:22:59.000 --> 00:23:01.413
If you just eliminate
variables.

00:23:01.413 --> 00:23:05.149
We are going to eliminate one
of these variables.

00:23:05.149 --> 00:23:08.808
Let's eliminate T2.
You could also eliminate T1.

00:23:08.808 --> 00:23:13.479
The main thing is eliminate one
