Why do I want to get rid of T1?
Well, I can add them.

00:23:33.229 --> 00:23:36.645
But, on the left-hand side,
I will have T1 prime plus T2

00:23:36.645 --> 00:23:39.006
prime. What good is that?

00:23:39.006 --> 00:23:40.000
[LAUGHTER]

