00:29:36.136 --> 00:29:38.712
And why must this system be
stable?

00:29:38.712 --> 00:29:42.196
In other words,
the long-term solutions must be

00:29:42.196 --> 00:29:45.530
zero, must all go to zero,
whatever they are.

00:29:45.530 --> 00:29:48.636
Why is that?
Well, because you are putting

00:29:48.636 --> 00:29:52.500
