physically.

00:30:08.512 --> 00:30:10.572
That's obvious.
And, therefore,

00:30:10.572 --> 00:30:14.210
the differential equation must
have the same property,

00:30:14.210 --> 00:30:17.848
and that means that its
coefficients must be positive.

00:30:17.848 --> 00:30:20.389
All its coefficients must be
